<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-39-0288 </DOCNO><TEXT>Each participant of the Third Pisa Meeting on Advanced Detectors had receiveda questionnaire prepared by S.R. Amendolia under the supervision of L.Stringa, convenor of the round-table. The questionnaires addressed themost important points in the technical and economical aspects of highenergy physics experiments, with the scope of focusing on the interactionof the industrial world with the pure research branch which the participantsrepresented. The questionnaires were elaborated and shown as an introductorytalk to the round-table.</TEXT></DOC>